  <body>
    <p>One of the most useful features in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode is the content
      completion support. It offers a list of elements, attributes, attribute values, and other
      options that are valid in the current editing context.
      <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>The fastest way to
      <?oxy_comment_start author="george" timestamp="20160330T095754+0300" comment="Here we use invoke, and later on we say activate for the same function, showing the content completion window." flag="done"?><?oxy_delete author="bogdan" timestamp="20160331T102726+0300" flag="done" content="invoke"?><?oxy_comment_end?><?oxy_insert_start author="bogdan" timestamp="20160331T102730+0300" flag="done"?>activate<?oxy_insert_end?>
      the <wintitle>Content Completion Assistant</wintitle> is to press <uicontrol
        conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/enter"/> or <uicontrol
        conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_space"/> in the editor
      panel.<?oxy_custom_end?></p>
